msg: Jena now depends on ARQ v2.8.0. The assembly.xml also includes the dependend jars using <dependencySets> rather than the content of the lib directory. mvn dependency:copy-dependencies can be used to update the content of the lib directory, it does not delete old jars, though. .classpath needs to be updated manually for now.
